Package gov.nasa.ial.mde.math

Provides classes for math functions and representations.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AngleModel The AngleModel class models angles in radians and degrees.
Bounds The Bounds class is an encapsulation of the left, right, top, and bottom bound (double) values.
Formulas A class for representing Formulas.
IntervalXY The IntervalXY class represents an interval between two points.
Matrix The Matrix class represents a matrix.
MdeNumberFormat The MDE Number Format.
MultiPointXY A generalization of the PointXY class that includes the idea of multiple (or no) y values corresponding to a given x.
NumberModel A model of a number.
PNom The PNom class represents a Polynomial in terms of its coefficients
PointRT This class represents a Polar point with double r and theta values.
PointXY This class represents a point with double x and y values.
RealZero The RealZero class represents a real zero.
Roots The Roots represent of a polynomial.
Roots.RootFactor The RootFactor represents the root factors.
SymbolicMatrix The SymbolicMatrix represents a symbolic matrix.
 

Package gov.nasa.ial.mde.math Description
